{"tid":2298934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港政府最叻係咩？咪就係 Reinvent the wheel","createTime":"2020-11-24T11:37:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T14:11:36.000Z","uid":261647,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4046803f1973180a1e438e50803c0c85d046dc7","tid":2298934,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/3740079936031712/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.907682852604782%2F3740079936031712%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=c08c291f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.907682852604782/3740079936031712/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：前線科技人員<br />\n <br />\n香港政府最叻係咩？咪就係 Reinvent the wheel<br />\n<br />\n當 Uber 已經有一套成功同受市場歡迎嘅 business model，香港政府走去抄啲唔抄啲，整套「專營的士」出嚟，拖咗幾年，最近仲胎死腹中。<br />\n<br />\n然後武肺殺到嚟，政府話俾你知的士司機係高危群組，因為佢哋追查唔到接觸過咩人？<br />\n<br />\nHello？一早合法化 Uber 今日咪唔駛煩囉。<br />\n<br />\n「安心出行」又係另一個例子。明明 Google Apple 已經整咗套 Exposure Notifications System， 用 Bluetooth #自動偵測 接觸過咩人兼且保護私隱，香港政府又走去 reinvent the wheel，用史前技術整套 QR Code 系統，要啲人主動走去 Scan 佢，仲要記得走嘅時候去 Logout。<br />\n<br />\nHello？啲人會記得嘅機會係零囉。<br />\n<br />\nExposure Notifications System 的介紹：<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.google/docum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fdocum&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=71e1033f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blog.google/docum</a><br />\nents/66/Overview_of_COVID-19_Contact_Tracing_Using_BLE_1.pdf<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5xpUGbe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5xpUGbe.png&h=5cfad240&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"462d81fa4ee88b1e5060426f6f9397e8a1209fbf","tid":2298934,"uid":200211,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:42:48.000Z","msg":"一講政府就勞氣<br />\n咁撚蠢"},{"pid":"c4255bcb197d707a9f221de2e8bebb6658fe8b5a","tid":2298934,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"喂你唔好批鬥政府好喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f93c79acffb4026fc860e20b13ad3607f1d2285","tid":2298934,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T11:52:13.000Z","msg":"公務員正常發揮啦"},{"pid":"e0019a6e3d627e22ba3095b31b1891a991c06945","tid":2298934,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用史前技術整套 QR Code 系統，要啲人主動走去 Scan 佢，仲要記得走嘅時候去 Logout。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nQR Code 係日本人以前發明<br />\n<br />\n香港班官一直鳩吹支付寶用 QR Code 係「好先進」<br />\n<br />\n咪堅持去用囉<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界有多大？ 佢地對眼只係向北望，其他嘢睇唔撚到架啦"},{"pid":"be2bb89fb4221a9c1adb3fcf360e0ec040ade388","tid":2298934,"uid":262035,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"因為港共重點唔係防疫而係要做監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333b93a1ab49554612a31a611bf77f15d63a78f6","tid":2298934,"uid":261773,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be2bb89fb4221a9c1adb3fcf360e0ec040ade388","tid":2298934,"uid":262035,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"因為港共重點唔係防疫而係要做監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"正解，not a bug but a feature <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGoogle / Apple 就設計到佢privacy為中心，而港共政府就係設計到佢無privacy 為中心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58932861cbd68666e19ca4ad6b32a3dbc386c1e5","tid":2298934,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:55:32.000Z","msg":"其實你追返確診者既八達通<br />\n<br />\n就知佢地去過邊<br />\n<br />\n再叫八達通公司掃埋差唔多時間出現既八達通交易<br />\n<br />\n就搵到其他人"},{"pid":"32200be6d17b989cd1efd8dca9d9ccb552a32865","tid":2298934,"uid":241399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"我諗最需要追踪果班<br />\n一係無電話<br />\n一係用華為"},{"pid":"664539554b2e89a2ec8d38fc984106d140506b49","tid":2298934,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"be2bb89fb4221a9c1adb3fcf360e0ec040ade388","tid":2298934,"uid":262035,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T13:19:56.000Z","msg":"因為港共重點唔係防疫而係要做監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"死都唔封關就係為左有藉口整多d監控設施<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以抗疫其實等於抗共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣諗係咪無咁易抗疫疲勞？"}]}